# Per-env tfvars may carry live secrets (keycloak_client_secret, smtp_password).
# Ignore all *.tfvars so staging.tfvars / prod.tfvars can never be committed,
# but keep the example template and the secret-free local-dev tfvars tracked.
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
!dev.tfvars

.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
